title: Farm Income for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1939-1945 (2)--Seasonally Adjusted Data, 1946-1968. Quarterly Figures Were Multiplied By Four To Derive Totals At Annual Rates. Source: 1954 Supplement To The Survey Of Current Business, National Income.

This NBER data series q08276a appears on the NBER website in Chapter 8 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter08.html.
